   Function used to calculate K gain for LQ control applications.
   Requires inclusion of "BasicLinearAlgebra" library to work.

   Usage:
   K = getGainLQ(A,B,Q,R);

   Where K,A,B,Q,R are BLA::Matrix<rows,columns> matrix objects.

